    "To mitigate this vulnerability, additional privacypreserving techniques such as differential privacy or secure aggregation can be employed.",
    "Furthermore, there are concerns about the collection of proxy samples to transfer knowledge between clients.",
    "This could potentially lead to breaches of privacy and security, as well as ethical concerns regarding informed consent and data ownership.",
    "In summary, while the proposed federated distillation framework has great potential for facilitating collaborative learning among multiple clients, it is important to be aware of the potential risks and take measures to ensure that the technology is used ethically and responsibly.",
